parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to catch fire, resulting in a potential safety risk to occupants and bystanders.
symptoms: None reported
as the recall was issued before any failures occurred.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the infotainment system can cause distraction while driving, leading to potential accidents.
symptoms: The center console display unit acts as though "ghost fingers" are continuously exercising the display
causing unintended actions such as turning climate controls on and off
attempting to delete phone contacts
and flickering navigation screens.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The hybrid battery can catch fire, resulting in a potential safety risk to occupants and bystanders.
symptoms: Red light coming from the charging cord receptacle
burning smell
and fire damage to the receptacle box.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Vehicle Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle can stall and lose power while driving, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle turns off randomly in traffic
with all warning lights turning on
and the vehicle fully shutting down and requiring a restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rear Camera and Parking Sensor Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the rear camera and parking sensors can increase the risk of accidents while reversing.
symptoms: The rear camera comes on
but parking assist
rear sensors
and cross-traffic sensors do not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission flex plate can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or fail to start, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Rattling noise coming from the transmission area
loss of power
vehicle stalling or failing to start
abnormal knocking sound
transmission slipping while changing gears
overheating engine
and check engine warning light illumination.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission shifting issues can cause the vehicle to hesitate, stall, or fail to accelerate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle hesitating or failing to accelerate
transmission slipping or hesitation
rough shifting
vehicle stalling or failing to start
and check engine warning light illumination.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shifter cable bushing can cause the vehicle to shift into park or neutral unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle shifting into park or neutral unexpectedly
wrench symbol display
system malfunction warning
and power train malfunction warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission/shift-related issues can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts into gear unexpectedly
the dial box reverts back to park after changing gears
the vehicle pulls to the right when accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hybrid system can cause the vehicle to lose fuel efficiency, leading to increased fuel costs and decreased performance.
symptoms: The vehicle is unable to use hybrid mode
the vehicle's fuel efficiency is significantly reduced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle's GPS and Bluetooth command button stop working
updates fail to resolve the issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the flexplate can cause the vehicle to make loud noises, leading to decreased performance and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle makes a loud noise when idle or driving in reverse.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The deterioration of the rear backblast felt cover can cause health risks and create a mess.
symptoms: The felt cover deteriorates
releasing tiny pieces that can be harmful if inhaled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended vehicle movement can cause accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle moves forward unexpectedly when shifting into reverse
the vehicle rolls backwards down a hill.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine/exhaust system can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: White smoke comes out of the hood
there is a smell of burned rubber.
